{
  "stem": "6526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many of the Jews wanted to be foreman, not so much they wanted not to work, but at least take away the meanness of the Poles and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when they came over to say, why didn't you do this, they didn't say, why you didn't do it, they just hit them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Mienia?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Mienia, I was there since, let's say, September maybe 25th of '42 till about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] till about the end of November-- till about the end of November.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in December, the Germans let the camps go, and they re-established Kaluszyn as another ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought all the people there were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Instead of-- they pulled them from each camp, Treblinka, or wherever they were sending them, they took all the Jews into one place and now we got them all at once.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back to the ghetto, December 1.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They established a ghetto that all the Jews that live in the area had to be in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they'll be found outside, they'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So many of them were hiding and they still came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were there nine days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We being, we Jews, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was sent in September to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never saw my mother and my sister again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother ran away one area, one place separately, and I ran to Mienia, to another place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we both came back to Kaluszyn on December 9-- on December 1.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a room, maybe 15, 20 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were apartments-- the apartment, two, three rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The two, three rooms consisted of a kitchen and a bedroom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no such thing as a lot of room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anybody that had a place to lay down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
